data.description: 3 Br 2 FBA Home on .39 Acres Off Southport Rd. Very Lg. Backyard With Deck and Storage Barn. Eat In Kitchen Off Of Living Room. Master Bedroom Has Master Bath Attached With Walk In Shower. 2 Car Garage With Work Bench, Hvac And W/H - 2017, Garage Door Opener - 2008, Wall Heater, Utility Wash Sink, Washer/Electric Dryer Hook Up And Service Door. Asphalt Drive With 2 Extra Parking Bays. Home Is Moments From Groceries, Restaurants, Retail Shopping. Desirable area near 65 only minutes from downtown. This one won't last long! Book a showing today!!
